疯狂P歌手丹妮尔摩尔的家人在自杀调查后发表声明：“人类善良和慷慨精神的形象” https://www.nme.com/news/music/crazy-p-singer-danielle-moores-family-release-statement-after-suicide-inquest-the-image-of- human-kindness-and-generosity- of-spirit-3829695?u tm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=疯狂p歌手丹妮尔摩尔斯家庭释放声明自杀调查后人类善良和慷慨精神的形象Elizabeth AubreyThu, 16 Jan 2025 20:19:56 +0000 Music NewsNews..IndieLet’s Talk – mental healthhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3829695 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Crazy P 的丹妮尔·摩尔" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “丹妮尔非常关心他人以及她所生活的世界的福祉”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/crazy-p-singer-danielle-moores-family-release-statement-after-suicide-inquest-the-image-of-human-kindness-and-generosity-of-spirit-3829695">疯狂P歌手丹妮尔摩尔的家人在自杀调查后发表声明：“人类善良和慷慨精神的形象”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Crazy P 的丹妮尔·摩尔" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Danielle-Moore-of-Crazy-P-CREDIT-Photo-by-Andrew-Benge_Redferns-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/crazy-p">Crazy P</a>歌手丹妮尔·摩尔 (Danielle Moore) 的家人在对她的死亡进行调查后发表了一份声明。</p><p>摩尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-after-death-of-beautiful-soul-danielle-moore-of-crazy-p-3789791">于去年 8 月去世，享年 52 岁，她的乐队成员最初于 9 月 2 日宣布了她去世的消息</a>。他们将她的死亡描述为“突然而悲惨”，并补充道：“我们非常悲痛地宣布这个令人难以置信和令人震惊的消息，我们美丽的丹妮尔·摩尔在突然而悲惨的情况下去世了。”</p><p>现在，验尸官报告称这位音乐家<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/lets-talk">自杀</a>身亡后，摩尔的家人发表了一份声明。</p><p>丹妮尔·摩尔的丈夫詹姆斯·恩塞尔向媒体发表了一份“为并代表她的家人”撰写的声明，他说：“虽然这个结论是意料之中的，但它仍然面临着挑战。我们仍然沉浸在失去她的痛苦之中，无法理解她已经离开了。虽然我们永远无法完全理解丹妮尔为何自杀，但我们知道她的死因与她生前的身份无关。</p><p> “丹妮尔非常关心他人以及她所生活的世界的福祉。她对社会不公正和消费主义的影响感到痛苦。她是一位富有同情心的人，本能地富有同情心和忠诚，与生活中的人们建立了最真实的联系。人类善良、慷慨的精神形象。</p><p> “我们也知道丹妮尔永远不会希望其他人得到这样的结果。她在遥远的过去克服了两次严重的精神疾病，并且非常感激自己做到了。在支持和治疗下，丹妮尔度过了当时看来无法忍受的事情，并希望继续生活。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permal